		width: 100%;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.license-text {
		background: #f5f0e8;
		padding: 4rem 3rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1.25rem;
		text-align: center;
		width: 100%;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}
